Table.Name: Software - Cloud Radial Installed
Table.SQL: Select DISTINCT Computers.ComputerID, Clients.Name as `Client Name`, Computers.Name as `Computer Name`, Computers.Domain, Computers.UserName as `Username`, Services.`Name` as `Services_Name` From Computers, Clients, Services Where Computers.ClientID = Clients.ClientID and Services.ComputerID = Computers.ComputerID and ((Services.`Name` = 'CloudRadial'))
